comment: Gasol (CHI) firms up as he sets the screen on Belinelli (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Cousins (SAC) makes incidental contact with Moore (CHI) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Cousins (SAC) makes incidental contact with Moore's (CHI) arm that does not affect his ability to complete the pass.
RATR shows that Gasol (CHI) makes incidental contact with Cousins' (SAC) non-shooting arm that does not affect his dunk attempt.
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Rose (CHI).
Moore (CHI) makes contact with Belinelli's (SAC) body on his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Belinelli (SAC) was behind the three point line when he was fouled by Moore (CHI) was confirmed.
Moore (CHI) makes contact with Belinelli (SAC) and affects his FOM away from the ball.
Rondo (SAC) cleanly knocks the ball away from Rose (CHI).
Gibson (CHI) makes contact with Cousins' (SAC) arm that affects his putback layup attempt.
Cousins (SAC) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Moore's (CHI) driving layup attempt.
Rondo (SAC) and Gibson (CHI) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Cousins (SAC) sets the screen on Moore (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Snell (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Cousins' (SAC) post move and shot attempt. The contact on the play is initiated by Cousins.
Snell (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Cousins' (SAC) shot attempt.
Belinelli (SAC) makes body to body contact with Moore (CHI) after he secures the loose ball.
Moore (CHI) and Belinelli (SAC) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
Cousins' (SAC) second FT does not make contact with the basket ring.
Rose (CHI) and Rondo (SAC) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
Moore (CHI) commits a take foul on Cousins (SAC) prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Gay (SAC) commits a take foul on Gasol (CHI).
Gibson (CHI) legally contests Belinelli's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
